Opossum M1 GABAergic SCT Types


library(Seurat)
library(reticulate)
library(arrow)
library(ggplot2)
library(dplyr)
library(SeuratDisk)
obj.opossum.gabaergic <- LoadH5Seurat("E:/Opossum_M1/seurat/opossum_m1_gabaergic.h5Seurat")


obj.opossum.gabaergic <- SCTransform(obj.opossum.gabaergic, vst.flavor = "v2", verbose = FALSE) %>%
               RunPCA(npcs = 30, verbose = FALSE) %>%
               RunUMAP(reduction = "pca", dims = 1:30, verbose = FALSE) %>%
               FindNeighbors(reduction = "pca", dims = 1:30, verbose = FALSE) %>%
               FindClusters(resolution = 1, algorithm = 4, method = "igraph")
